<h1 id="4å®ä¾‹">4.å®ä¾‹</h1>

<h4 id="åªæ‰“å°å“åº”å¤´éƒ¨ä¿¡æ¯">åªæ‰“å°å“åº”å¤´éƒ¨ä¿¡æ¯</h4>

<p>é€šè¿‡-Iæˆ–è€…-headå¯ä»¥åªæ‰“å°å‡ºHTTPå¤´éƒ¨ä¿¡æ¯</p>

<pre><code class="language-linux">curl -I http://man.linuxde.net

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Server: nginx/1.2.5
date: Mon, 10 Dec 2012 09:24:34 GMT
Content-Type: text/html; charset=UTF-8
Connection: keep-alive
Vary: Accept-Encoding
